%% Diagram: TCP HOL Blocking under HTTP/2
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Server
    participant Network
    participant Client

    Server->>Network: Segment 1 — stream 1 (CSS)
    Server->>Network: Segment 2 — stream 3 (JS)
    Server->>Network: Segment 3 — stream 5 (image)

    Note over Network: Segment 1 is dropped

    Network->>Client: Segment 2 arrives — buffered by TCP
    Network->>Client: Segment 3 arrives — buffered by TCP

    Note over Client: TCP delivers in order, app sees nothing yet

    Note over Server,Client: ~1 RTT later (RTO or fast retransmit)

    Server->>Network: Segment 1 (retransmit)
    Network->>Client: Segment 1 arrives

    Client-->>Client: TCP releases segments 1, 2, 3 to HTTP/2 layer

    Note over Client: All three streams stalled by one lost segment
